reviews.text: Authentic Thai restaurant run by Thai couple. Aroy is the name of their little kid, Dee means mom in Thai. They knew each other in Hong Kong and later on started a restaurant together. Can be quite crowded at night especially on weekends, better make a reservation if you wanna be sure. BBQ bread is my favourite. Curry is good. Fried rice and noodle are so so.
Food is amazing. Service is very nice. The aunties there are very friendly and kind. The portions of food are quite large.

不好吃，不會再光顧。
冬陰公好咸
串燒燒得太焦
食材不新鮮
上菜慢，服務一般。燒烤八爪魚及牛肉串，牛肉串需時二十五分鐘，在三十分鐘後問，八爪魚仍在燒，未熟，不可上枱。到上枱時，八爪魚都係未熟。啤酒不夠冰凍。本人來說，永不會有下次。比一星才能發佈!實在連一星也不值!!!
